{"tid":715802,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機CPU(s835)對比notebook CPU(i7 8550u)測試","createTime":"2018-06-24T18:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T19:11:19.000Z","uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7993ad1ffbffbaf7ef1bf83f01ba687b1f0491b","tid":715802,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平台</span><br />\nPC (唔知咩cpu): <br />\nArch Linux<br />\nblender 2.79<br />\n<br />\nNotebook (i7 8550u): <br />\nArch Linux<br />\nblender 2.79<br />\n<br />\nNote 8 (s835): <br />\nTermux <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.termux&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.termux%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=46742065\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.termux&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\ndebian <a href=\"https://github.com/sp4rkie/debian-on-termux\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fsp4rkie%2Fdebian-on-termux&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2a7a1f16\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/sp4rkie/debian-on-termux</a><br />\nblender 2.78<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法</span><br />\nDownload &amp; unzip <a href=\"https://download.blender.org/demo/test/BMW27_2.blend.zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdownload.blender.org%2Fdemo%2Ftest%2FBMW27_2.blend.zip&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7266191a\" target=\"_blank\">https://download.blender.org/demo/test/BMW27_2.blend.zip</a><br />\n行句command, <code>$ blender -b bmw27_cpu.blend -x 1 -o //render -f 0</code><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖係用note 8畫出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://transfer.sh/CtTKg/a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransfer.sh%2FCtTKg%2Fa.png&h=712418f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"041de86b592ea